                    <div class="area-model">
                        <div class="area-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);">
                            <div class="area-cell shaded">1</div>
                            <div class="area-cell shaded">2</div>
                            <div class="area-cell shaded">3</div>
                            <div class="area-cell unshaded">4</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h4 style="margin-top: 30px;">Step 2: Now take ${makeFrac(2,3)} of those shaded parts</h4>
                    <p>We need to divide each part into 3 pieces and take 2 of them:</p>
                    <div class="area-model">
                        <div class="area-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);">
